        <h2>Cloudimate</h2>
        <h5>My largest scale project and first web-app, Cloudimate.</h5>
        <p>This project originated from an internship I took. It was built to help the company automate services in AWS and create a centrallized location for the organizations costs.
           After my internship, I needed a project I could display for employers to show that I am competent in web developement and so after receieving permission from my employer, I worked towards making the web app better.
